The surface roughness of GeSe monolayer along with the different annealing temperatures, i.e., 100 °C, 150 °C, 200 °C, 250 °C and 300 °C, respectively. The relaxed configurations are also presented, which were obtained from the calculations in a 3 × 3 supercell. In each plot of the configurations, the bond length of some Ge-Se bonds and the bond angles of Ge-Se-Ge or Se-Ge-Se are indicated.

